result.name: Pho Fa Vietnamese Noodle Specialist 花姐越南牛肉粉專門店

reviews.text:
Pho tends to taste the same everywhere... and I’ve had pho in Canada, US, Mexico, Taiwan, China. 

What was served today did not taste like pho. The spices were different and the broth was too light. The spring rolls were very salty in contrast to the pho which made them not enjoyable. Was thoroughly disappointed in the food here.
Slightly more generous serving of pho than your average Vietnamese in HK
Not many choices on the menu. The serving of noddle is less. Taste abd service are ok.
Not worth a try.
Dont eat the $68 tomata deluxr beef noodles.  The soup is sweet!  Expensive and not traditional taste.  But my friend's cambodia style noodles is ok

reviews.text: 好多時都係大叻滿座啲人就行過呢間度食，點解呢？ 係真係有原因嘅。 因為味道啦。 唔係好正宗嘅越南味啦。好處係坐位舒適，冇咁擠迫。

Pho tends to taste the same everywhere... and I’ve had pho in Canada, US, Mexico, Taiwan, China. 

What was served today did not taste like pho. The spices were different and the broth was too light. The spring rolls were very salty in contrast to the pho which made them not enjoyable. Was thoroughly disappointed in the food here.
Slightly more generous serving of pho than your average Vietnamese in HK
Not many choices on the menu. The serving of noddle is less. Taste abd service are ok.

位於灣仔蘭杜街的一間小店，
生牛肉湯河配牛油雞翼加凍飲共$70，牛肉不過不失而且份量足夠，湯底清甜帶有頗重香矛味，本人覺得很不錯，唯稍偏油了一點；牛油雞翼醃得夠味，表皮炸得十分脆，但有點過硬。
